sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client<br/>(via KServe Ingress)
    participant REST as REST Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant AB as Adaptive Batcher<br/>(optional)
    participant Cache as Response Cache<br/>(optional)
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lgbm/onnx)
    participant Worker as Worker Process<br/>(multiprocessing)
    participant Kafka as Kafka Server<br/>9092/TCP
    participant KafkaBroker as Kafka Brokers
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTel as OTel Collector

    Note over Client,Model: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP (plaintext, pod-internal)
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane handler
    DP->>Cache: Check response cache (if enabled)
    Cache-->>DP: Cache miss
    DP->>AB: Queue request (if batching enabled)
    AB->>Model: Batched predict() call
    Model-->>AB: Prediction result
    AB-->>DP: Individual response (UUID-matched)
    DP->>Cache: Store in cache
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Client: JSON Response (HTTP 200)

    Note over Client,Model: Flow 2: gRPC Streaming Inference
    Client->>gRPC: ModelStreamInfer<br/>gRPC (plaintext, pod-internal)
    gRPC->>DP: InferenceServicer handler
    DP->>Model: predict_stream() async iterator
    loop Streaming responses
        Model-->>DP: Partial result
        DP-->>gRPC: Stream response chunk
        gRPC-->>Client: gRPC stream message
    end

    Note over Worker,Model: Flow 3: Parallel Worker Inference
    DP->>Worker: Dispatch via multiprocessing.Queue<br/>(Pickle/IPC)
    Worker->>Model: predict() in worker process<br/>(bypasses GIL)
    Model-->>Worker: Prediction result
    Worker-->>DP: Response via Queue<br/>(Pickle/IPC)

    Note over Kafka,KafkaBroker: Flow 4: Kafka Async Inference
    KafkaBroker->>Kafka: Consume from input topic<br/>9092/TCP
    Kafka->>DP: DataPlane.infer()
    DP->>Model: predict()
    Model-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>Kafka: Response
    Kafka->>KafkaBroker: Produce to output topic<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Metrics,OTel: Observability Flows
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(request counts, latencies, batch queue)
    REST->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)
    gRPC->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)
